### Phase 3: ANALYZE (PROBLEM ANALYSIS)

```mermaid
graph TD
    Start["Begin Problem<br>Analysis"] --> LoadAnalyze["Load ANALYZE<br>Mode Rules"]
    LoadAnalyze --> DetectType["Detect Document<br>Type (Requirements/Bugs)"]
