```

**Steps:**
1. Load ANALYZE mode rules and templates
2. Detect document type based on task characteristics
3. Load appropriate analysis template (requirements or bugs primarily)
4. Conduct focused problem analysis using template
5. Document analysis results in memory-bank/analytics/ folder
6. Prepare analysis for planning phase consumption

